<br>
1. If you can fork over 40 a month for Stormhammer, then you should already have Luclin. If you dont, then you may want to get it.<br>
<br>
2. Easy to bank there.  I heard there is not penalty for carrying large amounts of cash. Ever try to walk while holding 30k in pp?  I hear that crawl doesnt exist in the Bazaar.<br>
<br>
3. Shorter distance to run to the bank.<br>
<br>
4. Im an Iksar, and I dont do Antonica factions...my choice, not asking for pity. There are many iksar like me. While the darkies have Neriak, and the Goods have Freeport, I have to have a cash cow which can be a pain in the ass.  Having it in Bazaar is a good idea to me.<br>
<br>
I voted Bazaar, and when I was running through EC last night I saw maybe 2 people looking to sell.<br>
<br>
